Upcoming event : Giving_Food to the Homeless - November 21 , 2015
What do you usually do on Saturday night ? Go for coffee with friends ? Chat-chit ? Spend time with your family ? ? ? Yes , a lot of things to do . BUT_WE_HAVE_A_VERY_SPECIAL_PROGRAM_FOR_YOU_TO_JOIN : Giving_Food to the Homeless on Saturday night November 21 , 2015 ( 17 : 00 we prepare the food ; 21 : 00 we go out and deliver to the homeless around HCMC )
Hereunder is our same previous event :
