The_Compassion in Vietnam_Club will organize this event again to give food to the homeless . We will cook chicken soup and deliver to homeless in HCMC also to the people who work during the night . It will be great if you can join us as volunteer to support the cooking and delivery , and also we are welcome all donations to this meaningful event . So , COME and JOIN with us ! ! ! ! ! Register via the Event_Link or send mesg to our FB .
